1
00:00:24,030 --> 00:00:25,290
[Adapted from a novel published on
Qidian Reading under China Literature]

2
00:00:25,320 --> 00:00:27,180
["Way of Choices" by Mao Ni]

3
00:00:28,300 --> 00:00:29,830
[Minors]

4
00:00:29,860 --> 00:00:31,550
[should watch with guardian consent]

5
00:02:14,100 --> 00:02:19,320
[Way of Choices]

6
00:02:21,120 --> 00:02:22,520
So you are Chen Changsheng?

7
00:02:21,180 --> 00:02:24,640
[Previously]

8
00:02:23,320 --> 00:02:24,050
Come up here.

9
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:25,840
I'm going to kill you!

10
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:27,440
You have no cultivation;

11
00:02:27,440 --> 00:02:28,770
I'll go up and fight him.

12
00:02:29,079 --> 00:02:30,000
He used poison?

13
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:31,820
You disgusting thing,

14
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:33,700
I'll whip that filthy mouth
right off your face!

15
00:02:33,700 --> 00:02:35,329
The poison is spreading
throughout his entire body.

16
00:02:35,329 --> 00:02:36,990
I have to stop it immediately.

17
00:02:37,290 --> 00:02:38,870
No matter who you are,

18
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:41,160
if you want to hurt my friend
and my disciple,

19
00:02:41,160 --> 00:02:42,560
I will destroy you first!

20
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:44,579
Congratulations!

21
00:02:44,640 --> 00:02:45,760
You have become the third student

22
00:02:45,760 --> 00:02:46,980
of the State Religious Academy!

23
00:02:46,980 --> 00:02:48,050
Bad news.

24
00:02:48,260 --> 00:02:49,500
Tomorrow, at the Qixi Festival,

25
00:02:49,500 --> 00:02:50,900
your fiancee Xu Yourong

26
00:02:51,300 --> 00:02:52,630
is going to get married.

27
00:02:58,880 --> 00:03:02,830
[Midland Continent]

28
00:02:59,600 --> 00:03:00,760
In the Midland Continent,

29
00:03:00,760 --> 00:03:02,820
Human, Yao, and Demon Races coexist.

30
00:03:03,760 --> 00:03:04,420
Among them,

31
00:03:04,480 --> 00:03:05,670
the Demon Race is the most powerful.

32
00:03:05,670 --> 00:03:08,080
They treat all beings as food and slaves.

33
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:14,040
From the Founding Emperor
to Emperor Taizong,

34
00:03:14,530 --> 00:03:16,040
after several northern campaigns,

35
00:03:16,040 --> 00:03:19,900
they finally managed to drive
the Demon Race back to the frozen north.

36
00:03:20,079 --> 00:03:20,600
However,

37
00:03:20,600 --> 00:03:22,260
to eliminate them completely,

38
00:03:22,260 --> 00:03:26,840
[The Northern Demon Race] [Grand Zhou]
[North-South Alliance] [Southern Realms]

39
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:25,930
the Grand Zhou Dynasty and
the Southern Realms needed to unite.

40
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:26,840
However,

41
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:29,620
Grand Zhou had Holy Empress Tianhai,

42
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:33,000
while the Southern Realms had
the Sword God Su Li.

43
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:34,520
Neither of the two invincible masters

44
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:36,200
was willing to bow their heads,

45
00:03:36,200 --> 00:03:38,260
which made the alliance impossible.

46
00:03:39,200 --> 00:03:40,079
Today,

47
00:03:40,340 --> 00:03:43,730
[Alliance by Marriage]

48
00:03:41,480 --> 00:03:43,680
we finally have the opportunity again!

49
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:46,760
Xu Yourong, daughter of
Divine General of the Grand Zhou,

50
00:03:46,760 --> 00:03:48,820
has awakened the True Phoenix Blood.

51
00:03:49,880 --> 00:03:52,640
And Qiushan Jun, the eldest disciple of
the Southern Sword God,

52
00:03:52,640 --> 00:03:54,640
has awakened the True Dragon Blood.

53
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:56,360
People all say

54
00:03:56,920 --> 00:03:58,600
that the True Dragon and the True Phoenix

55
00:03:58,600 --> 00:04:00,400
are a perfect match.

56
00:04:01,430 --> 00:04:05,580
[Betrothal Contract]

57
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:03,160
If they get married,

58
00:04:03,440 --> 00:04:05,780
they can promote the North-South Alliance.

59
00:04:05,780 --> 00:04:06,770
[Midland Continent] [Southern Realms]

60
00:04:06,870 --> 00:04:10,320
[Alliance]

61
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:12,930
It's only that in this case,

62
00:04:13,440 --> 00:04:14,520
your fiancee

63
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:16,680
will marry someone else.

64
00:04:29,700 --> 00:04:31,750
[Qixi Festival A pale moon in the vast sky
The Milky Way eternal in autumn]

65
00:04:31,770 --> 00:04:34,600
[Joy and sorrow mingle,
year after year on this night]

66
00:04:46,850 --> 00:04:47,740
[Read a book a hundred times,
and its meaning will reveal itself.]

67
00:04:47,820 --> 00:04:48,390
[Marrow Cleansing Theory]

68
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:50,440
I can't live long.

69
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:53,170
I don't know if I can change my fate yet.

70
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:56,940
I don't intend to bind Miss Xu
with the betrothal contract.

71
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:59,480
Should we succeed

72
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:00,970
in achieving the North-South Alliance
without bloodshed,

73
00:05:00,970 --> 00:05:02,300
it'd be most desirable.

74
00:05:02,760 --> 00:05:04,040
It is what everyone hopes for

75
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:05,520
and will celebrate.

76
00:05:06,640 --> 00:05:08,570
Everything would fall into place,

77
00:05:08,640 --> 00:05:09,640
just as it should.

78
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:17,580
However...

79
00:05:17,880 --> 00:05:18,880
I don't know why

80
00:05:20,440 --> 00:05:21,400
I still

81
00:05:22,200 --> 00:05:23,660
want to go see it in person.

82
00:05:24,780 --> 00:05:26,990
[I want to go see it]

83
00:05:27,020 --> 00:05:28,830
[The Young Director: Episode 5]

84
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:32,520
To formally propose the marriage
on the night of the Qixi Festival?

85
00:05:32,520 --> 00:05:35,050
The Southern Realms really
chose a good date.

86
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:37,240
After all, it's a big deal
for the North-South Alliance.

87
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:38,360
Everyone wants to come to
congratulate them

88
00:05:38,360 --> 00:05:39,480
and witness it with their own eyes.

89
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:40,800
It's quite lively.

90
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:43,720
The old foxes who don't
usually come out have come.

91
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:46,480
Prince Chen Liu is here!

92
00:05:48,400 --> 00:05:49,960
Even Chen, the royal family member, came!

93
00:05:49,960 --> 00:05:51,800
[Prince Chen Liu, Royal Family Member]

94
00:05:50,400 --> 00:05:53,840
The Holy Empress sent the Crown Prince
Chen Liu
as the witness to the marriage.

95
00:05:53,840 --> 00:05:55,840
-Don't cause trouble for Tiandao Academy.
-Welcome, Prince Chen Liu.

96
00:05:55,840 --> 00:05:57,900
Sorry for not greeting you properly.

97
00:05:58,040 --> 00:05:59,310
The True Phoenix from our Grand Zhou

98
00:05:59,310 --> 00:06:02,280
is going to marry Qiushan jun,
the True Dragon from the south.

99
00:06:02,280 --> 00:06:04,040
It symbolizes the North-South Alliance.

100
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:05,000
After tonight,

101
00:06:05,080 --> 00:06:07,440
I should call you Nation's Pillar.

102
00:06:07,640 --> 00:06:10,640
If my daughter's marriage
can benefit the Human Race,

103
00:06:10,640 --> 00:06:13,520
-it'll be our Xu family's honor.
-Cardinal Melisha

104
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:15,040
is here!

105
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,200
Cardinal.

106
00:06:16,200 --> 00:06:19,960
I read a fortune before I came out.

107
00:06:19,960 --> 00:06:21,200
Tonight

108
00:06:21,200 --> 00:06:23,720
is indeed an auspicious date.

109
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:24,760
Great!

110
00:06:24,960 --> 00:06:27,220
Every bigwig from the Continent is here.

111
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:28,400
Chen Changsheng,

112
00:06:28,400 --> 00:06:29,600
are you coming or not?

113
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:33,320
The marriage-proposal delegation
from the Southern Realms

114
00:06:33,320 --> 00:06:34,440
is here!

115
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:36,320
Look!

116
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:38,810
The delegation from the Southern Realms!

117
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:50,840
Is that the Lishan Sword Sect
of the Southern Realms?

118
00:06:49,820 --> 00:06:51,820
[Xiaosonggong, Grand Elder
of Lishan Sword Sect]

119
00:06:52,400 --> 00:06:55,170
It is said that seven disciples
of the Lishan Sword Sect are so gifted

120
00:06:55,170 --> 00:06:57,530
[Guan Feibai, Lishan Sword Sect]

121
00:06:55,280 --> 00:06:58,120
that they are known as
the Divine Nation's Seven Prodigies.

122
00:06:58,120 --> 00:07:00,040
Four of them came tonight.

123
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:01,960
[Liang Banhu, Lishan Sword Sect]

124
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:02,520
Is Qiushan Jun here?

125
00:07:02,520 --> 00:07:04,280
Why haven't I seen him?

126
00:07:03,630 --> 00:07:05,790
[Qi Jian, Lishan Sword Sect]

127
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:07,160
They're quite something there.

128
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:08,640
What an eye-opener!

129
00:07:07,350 --> 00:07:09,250
[Gou Hanshi, Lishan Sword Sect]

130
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:14,040
Those four must be the disciples
of the Lishan Sword Sect.

131
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:16,920
They have taken up six
of the top ten of the Blue Cloud List.

132
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:18,490
In Grand Zhou, Only Xu Yourong

133
00:07:18,490 --> 00:07:20,120
can compete with them.

134
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:23,040
I'm Xiaosonggong.

135
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:24,400
I, along with the Lishan disciples,

136
00:07:24,400 --> 00:07:26,360
am here to greet you, Divine General Xu.

137
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:28,640
I've heard so much about you,
Elder Xiaosonggong.

138
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:30,320
It's my great pleasure to meet you.

139
00:07:30,320 --> 00:07:31,400
Please come in.

140
00:07:31,840 --> 00:07:33,960
Qiushan Jun is still
fighting in the North.

141
00:07:33,960 --> 00:07:35,290
He hasn't returned yet.

142
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:37,800
He's fighting for our Human Race.

143
00:07:37,800 --> 00:07:39,720
No wonder the old man rushed to
pick on Chen Changsheng

144
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:41,250
as soon as he got to the city.

145
00:07:41,680 --> 00:07:42,440
Turns out

146
00:07:42,440 --> 00:07:46,370
he aimed to earn a reputation for
promoting the North-South Alliance.

147
00:07:49,440 --> 00:07:50,580
As expected of you, Sir.

148
00:07:50,580 --> 00:07:53,980
You look good even in
the State Religious Academy's uniform.

149
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:57,120
This is indeed the most important proposal
on the Continent.

150
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:58,000
So lively.

151
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:07,360
Princess of Ping

152
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:09,760
has something important
to discuss with you.

153
00:08:09,760 --> 00:08:11,290
Could you please follow me?

154
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:12,880
What important matter can she have?

155
00:08:12,880 --> 00:08:13,680
I'm not going.

156
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:15,660
I need to keep Master company.

157
00:08:16,360 --> 00:08:17,620
Since it's important,

158
00:08:17,840 --> 00:08:18,640
just go.

159
00:08:19,520 --> 00:08:20,850
Then, I'll be back soon.

160
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:22,760
Hurry up!

161
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:33,400
The North-South Alliance

162
00:08:33,400 --> 00:08:35,200
is vital to the future of the Human Race.

163
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:36,720
If you were smart enough,

164
00:08:36,799 --> 00:08:38,799
you wouldn't have shown up tonight.

165
00:08:39,039 --> 00:08:39,960
Miss Mo,

166
00:08:40,559 --> 00:08:41,690
you misunderstood.

167
00:08:41,760 --> 00:08:42,080
I...

168
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:43,640
I know this is unfair to you.

169
00:08:44,280 --> 00:08:45,560
But I warned you before

170
00:08:45,920 --> 00:08:48,680
that you shouldn't let anyone
know about your marriage contract.

171
00:08:48,680 --> 00:08:51,040
I never intended to use
this betrothal contract to bind Miss Xu.

172
00:08:51,040 --> 00:08:52,800
-I just want...
-It doesn't matter what you think.

173
00:08:52,800 --> 00:08:54,240
You are far too insignificant

174
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:55,900
compared to this grand cause!

175
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:01,080
What?

176
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:03,180
You asked me here just to catch up?

177
00:09:03,500 --> 00:09:05,520
[Princess of Ping]

178
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:07,800
If this is the important matter
you mentioned,

179
00:09:07,800 --> 00:09:09,860
I'm afraid I can't accompany you now.

180
00:09:12,460 --> 00:09:15,770
[Seal]

181
00:09:17,520 --> 00:09:18,960
You want to harm Master.

182
00:09:19,520 --> 00:09:20,600
But I remember...

183
00:09:21,060 --> 00:09:23,660
you've liked Qiushan Jun
since you were young.

184
00:09:23,680 --> 00:09:25,080
I'm a princess after all.

185
00:09:25,680 --> 00:09:27,740
I have to do something for Grand Zhou.

186
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:28,840
I knew it.

187
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:35,320
I can't beat you.

188
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:36,680
But…

189
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:38,600
if you hurt me here,

190
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:40,530
can the Bai family bear the consequences?

191
00:09:39,780 --> 00:09:46,920
[Seal]

192
00:09:40,640 --> 00:09:42,080
If something happens to me here,

193
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:43,440
you can't afford it, either, can you?

194
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:44,280
Are you crazy?

195
00:09:51,160 --> 00:09:53,400
If Xu Yourong hadn't written
to protect you,

196
00:09:53,400 --> 00:09:55,120
I would have killed you now.

197
00:09:55,720 --> 00:09:57,320
Nothing unexpected can happen tonight.

198
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:58,800
Stay here if you're wise.

199
00:09:58,920 --> 00:10:00,640
Don't come out and mess around again.

200
00:10:00,640 --> 00:10:01,440
This is...

201
00:10:01,720 --> 00:10:02,640
a formation!

202
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:10,920
Congratulations, Uncle Xu.

203
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:13,940
Your Highness.

204
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,200
Here's to you.

205
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:17,560
To our great alliance.

206
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:24,600
Why?

207
00:10:25,040 --> 00:10:26,680
Everyone guards against me.

208
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:32,600
The proposal ceremony in Grand Zhou

209
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:33,840
has two rituals:
the Three Gifts of the Wild Goose

210
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:36,300
and the Three Questions
to Heaven and Earth.

211
00:10:36,520 --> 00:10:38,520
If I can reach Weiyang Palace
before the ceremony is over,

212
00:10:38,520 --> 00:10:39,600
it may not be too late

213
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:40,870
for what I intend to do.

214
00:10:41,680 --> 00:10:42,440
White rocks.

215
00:10:42,880 --> 00:10:43,600
A plum tree.

216
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:45,160
A cold pool.

217
00:10:45,680 --> 00:10:47,810
Could it be the Tong Palace Formation?

218
00:10:48,510 --> 00:10:49,880
Treatise on the Origins
of the Various Halls,

219
00:10:49,880 --> 00:10:50,880
Compendium of Formations,

220
00:10:50,880 --> 00:10:54,200
and The Story of the Southern Bough
all have records of this.

221
00:10:54,200 --> 00:10:55,680
When the Founding Emperor
rebelled against the previous dynasty,

222
00:10:55,680 --> 00:10:58,720
he imprisoned the previous emperor
in the Tong Palace until his death.

223
00:10:58,720 --> 00:11:00,680
The reigning Grand Pontiff founded

224
00:11:00,680 --> 00:11:03,000
the Tong Palace Formation under this name.

225
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:03,640
Found it!

226
00:11:03,820 --> 00:11:05,730
[Tong Palace Formation]

227
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:06,120
When Emperor Taizong ruled the country,

228
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:08,520
He once proposed improving the formation.

229
00:11:10,280 --> 00:11:11,800
The executor was

230
00:11:11,920 --> 00:11:13,440
Wang Zhice,

231
00:11:14,640 --> 00:11:15,880
one of the 24 Sages.

232
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:18,360
The way I'm looking for to change my fate

233
00:11:18,360 --> 00:11:19,620
is also related to him.

234
00:11:21,120 --> 00:11:22,640
The formation can't be broken

235
00:11:22,640 --> 00:11:24,440
in the Following the Sage Realm.

236
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:27,560
But 500 years ago,

237
00:11:27,760 --> 00:11:29,960
a Cardinal, invited by Emperor Taizong,

238
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:31,480
succeeded in breaking this formation.

239
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:33,160
He also left a comment.

240
00:11:34,240 --> 00:11:36,400
I really miss it.

241
00:11:37,360 --> 00:11:40,520
An old friend invited me
to break a formation.

242
00:11:40,520 --> 00:11:44,600
I planted a plum tree
at the eye of the formation.

243
00:11:45,400 --> 00:11:46,520
By now,

244
00:11:46,520 --> 00:11:48,720
that tree should be in bloom.

245
00:11:48,740 --> 00:11:52,940
[Seal]

246
00:11:50,600 --> 00:11:51,200
Forget it.

247
00:11:51,840 --> 00:11:52,520
Just leave.

248
00:11:54,360 --> 00:11:56,560
But it's useless for you to go there now.

249
00:11:56,920 --> 00:11:58,360
I'm afraid Chen Changsheng

250
00:11:58,360 --> 00:12:00,400
won't make it for the banquet.

251
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:02,480
No matter what trap you have set,

252
00:12:02,480 --> 00:12:03,880
Master will break it!

253
00:12:04,280 --> 00:12:05,040
Wait and see.

254
00:12:05,220 --> 00:12:06,010
He said,

255
00:12:06,440 --> 00:12:07,480
"Two trees make a forest.

256
00:12:06,600 --> 00:12:09,330
[Two trees make a forest.
Stars are the lights.]

257
00:12:07,800 --> 00:12:09,060
Stars are the lights."

258
00:12:09,160 --> 00:12:10,680
When wind gives rise to water,

259
00:12:10,680 --> 00:12:12,280
a Gateway to Life can be seen.

260
00:12:12,920 --> 00:12:15,120
The plum tree is the eye of the formation.

261
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:16,050
It's also a hint.

262
00:12:17,440 --> 00:12:19,440
By using the stars in the night sky
as reference points,

263
00:12:19,440 --> 00:12:21,170
one can deduce the path to life.

264
00:12:22,880 --> 00:12:24,040
Start from a single tree.

265
00:12:23,480 --> 00:12:25,010
[The plum tree is the starting point]

266
00:12:24,230 --> 00:12:25,520
The plum tree is the single tree here.

267
00:12:25,520 --> 00:12:26,480
Wood generates great fire.

268
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:27,680
Then, proceed to the Heart Mansion.

269
00:12:27,680 --> 00:12:29,040
The Heart Mansion governs fire.

270
00:12:29,040 --> 00:12:30,440
Fire generates thick earth.

271
00:12:30,440 --> 00:12:31,240
Then, advance to the Dipper Mansion.

272
00:12:30,650 --> 00:12:31,970
[Dipper Mansion]

273
00:12:32,340 --> 00:12:33,920
Wait until the twin trees are seen,

274
00:12:33,920 --> 00:12:35,980
and one may enter the Gateway to Life.

275
00:12:38,500 --> 00:12:39,110
[Void Mansion]

276
00:12:43,520 --> 00:12:44,560
Why did I fail?

277
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:47,160
The star positions on the water's surface
weren't counted.

278
00:12:47,160 --> 00:12:49,220
The water's surface is like a mirror.

279
00:12:50,140 --> 00:12:51,280
I see.

280
00:12:51,300 --> 00:12:53,040
I'll do it again.

281
00:12:53,720 --> 00:12:55,390
The Dipper Mansion marks metal.

282
00:12:55,390 --> 00:12:56,510
Metal moves three positions west.

283
00:12:56,510 --> 00:12:58,110
It lights up the Kui Mansion.

284
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:05,080
Again!

285
00:13:10,400 --> 00:13:11,440
The Ji Mansion governs wind.

286
00:13:10,620 --> 00:13:11,330
[Ji Mansion]

287
00:13:11,440 --> 00:13:12,680
Wind gives rise to water.

288
00:13:12,680 --> 00:13:14,940
Water reflects the tree into twin forms.

289
00:13:14,950 --> 00:13:16,120
Only one last step,

290
00:13:16,170 --> 00:13:17,430
and I'll turn the tide.

291
00:13:22,400 --> 00:13:23,160
Got it.

292
00:13:30,040 --> 00:13:31,280
Two trees make a forest.

293
00:13:30,250 --> 00:13:31,570
[Two trees make a forest.]

294
00:13:31,480 --> 00:13:32,960
The Gateway to Life is here!

295
00:13:31,760 --> 00:13:33,350
[The Gateway to Life is here.]

296
00:13:57,480 --> 00:13:59,200
Interesting kid.

297
00:13:59,720 --> 00:14:02,160
He broke Wang Zhice's formation, too.

298
00:14:02,640 --> 00:14:03,680
However,

299
00:14:03,680 --> 00:14:05,440
because of that incident,

300
00:14:05,440 --> 00:14:07,720
Wang Zhice made some adjustments to it.

301
00:14:08,360 --> 00:14:10,200
What was once the Gateway to Life,

302
00:14:10,200 --> 00:14:12,600
is now the Gateway to Death.

303
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:16,200
I should be out of the Tong Palace by now.

304
00:14:16,240 --> 00:14:17,770
What is this place?

305
00:14:18,240 --> 00:14:19,440
There's so much gold.

306
00:14:19,800 --> 00:14:21,200
Could it be the treasury?

307
00:14:40,960 --> 00:14:41,760
That is...

308
00:14:42,540 --> 00:14:43,340
A dragon?

309
00:14:50,720 --> 00:14:51,800
The auspicious hour

310
00:14:51,800 --> 00:14:53,120
has arrived!

311
00:14:53,280 --> 00:14:55,200
I invite all of you present

312
00:14:55,440 --> 00:14:56,770
to witness it together.

313
00:14:56,880 --> 00:14:58,080
The engagement ceremony

314
00:14:58,080 --> 00:15:00,120
starts now!

315
00:15:00,760 --> 00:15:03,080
Proposal starts!

316
00:15:03,200 --> 00:15:04,800
I'm Xiaosonggong.

317
00:15:04,920 --> 00:15:09,000
On behalf of the Lishan Sword Sect,
I came to propose marriage.

318
00:15:09,320 --> 00:15:11,840
I come on behalf of Qiu Shanjun,
disciple of our Sect,

319
00:15:11,840 --> 00:15:12,840
to seek the hand in marriage

320
00:15:12,840 --> 00:15:15,970
of Xu Yourong, noble lady
of the Divine General's Estate

321
00:15:16,000 --> 00:15:17,600
of Grand Zhou.

322
00:15:18,160 --> 00:15:20,600
The wild goose is the gift.

323
00:15:21,040 --> 00:15:24,000
The betrothal gift includes
a messenger goose

324
00:15:24,120 --> 00:15:25,760
and countless treasures,

325
00:15:25,760 --> 00:15:27,640
with sincerity.

326
00:15:27,700 --> 00:15:30,900
[Divine General of the East, Xu Shiji]
[Head of Qiushan Family, Qiushan Yuanxin]

327
00:15:27,920 --> 00:15:29,440
The two parties pledge in writing.

328
00:15:29,440 --> 00:15:31,120
A written covenant binds the union.

329
00:15:31,120 --> 00:15:32,980
The imperial seal bears witness.

330
00:15:33,040 --> 00:15:35,640
Heaven's mandate is the matchmaker.

331
00:15:36,320 --> 00:15:38,120
Once the Human Race
achieved the North-South Alliance,

332
00:15:38,120 --> 00:15:38,990
it's only a matter of time before
we can attack the Demon Race

333
00:15:38,990 --> 00:15:40,800
and conquer Snow Old City.

334
00:15:40,800 --> 00:15:41,400
Yes.

335
00:15:41,400 --> 00:15:42,480
Now,

336
00:15:42,480 --> 00:15:44,760
the Three Questions to Heaven and Earth.

337
00:15:45,520 --> 00:15:47,840
The ceremony will be completed after
the Three Questions to Heaven and Earth.

338
00:15:47,840 --> 00:15:50,100
Chen Changsheng, where on earth are you?

339
00:15:50,480 --> 00:15:51,480
If you don't come,

340
00:15:51,680 --> 00:15:53,040
it'll be too late!

341
00:15:55,480 --> 00:15:57,080
According to
The Three Thousand Daoist Scriptures,

342
00:15:57,080 --> 00:15:58,480
Dragon is a sign of death.

343
00:16:00,840 --> 00:16:02,510
It seems that Master is right.

344
00:16:03,040 --> 00:16:03,760
My fate

345
00:16:04,280 --> 00:16:05,240
is really bad.

346
00:16:24,360 --> 00:16:26,560
The Dragon Race reveres
the Golden Giant Dragon as supreme.

347
00:16:26,560 --> 00:16:27,320
This sword

348
00:16:27,560 --> 00:16:29,960
is forged by the Golden Dragon's Whiskers.

349
00:16:32,360 --> 00:16:34,760
Could this be intra-race rank oppression?

350
00:16:40,080 --> 00:16:40,800
This is

351
00:16:41,120 --> 00:16:43,480
Wang Zhice's
Double-Spiritual Dragon-Locking Formation.

352
00:16:43,480 --> 00:16:44,430
Is this dragon

353
00:16:44,880 --> 00:16:46,360
imprisoned here by him?

354
00:16:52,650 --> 00:16:55,330
This Dragon's nest is connected
to Shendu's Earth Veins.

355
00:16:55,330 --> 00:16:56,650
That is the exit.

356
00:16:57,080 --> 00:16:57,760
It's just…

357
00:16:57,920 --> 00:16:58,840
it's too high.

358
00:17:03,070 --> 00:17:04,089
Sain.

359
00:17:03,220 --> 00:17:05,599
[Hello]

360
00:17:07,470 --> 00:17:09,359
Qi haan hun?

361
00:17:07,990 --> 00:17:10,140
[You speak dragon language?]

362
00:17:11,040 --> 00:17:13,079
I only know the pronunciation
of the dragon language,

363
00:17:13,079 --> 00:17:14,680
but I don't know its meaning.

364
00:17:14,800 --> 00:17:16,530
Master didn't teach me the last scroll of

365
00:17:16,530 --> 00:17:18,119
The Three Thousand Daoist Scriptures.

366
00:17:18,119 --> 00:17:19,950
[Get lost]

367
00:17:19,119 --> 00:17:19,720
Senior.

368
00:17:20,270 --> 00:17:21,780
We are both trapped here.

369
00:17:22,359 --> 00:17:23,839
Since you don't plan to eat me,

370
00:17:23,839 --> 00:17:24,920
can you help me out?

371
00:17:28,480 --> 00:17:29,400
In exchange,

372
00:17:29,500 --> 00:17:30,670
I will come back

373
00:17:30,700 --> 00:17:32,030
to do something for you.

374
00:17:33,910 --> 00:17:35,970
Although my cultivation is not high,

375
00:17:36,440 --> 00:17:39,360
I had a way to break Master Zhice's
Tong Palace and come here,

376
00:17:39,360 --> 00:17:40,120
which means

377
00:17:40,160 --> 00:17:42,420
maybe there's something I can do for you.

378
00:17:53,570 --> 00:17:55,160
[Dare to have a try?]

379
00:17:54,600 --> 00:17:55,520
I see.

380
00:17:55,520 --> 00:17:56,580
Thank you, Senior.

381
00:18:16,360 --> 00:18:18,010
The Three Rites are over.

382
00:18:18,080 --> 00:18:21,210
There are only
Three Questions to Heaven and Earth left.

383
00:18:28,760 --> 00:18:29,720
It's the palace.

384
00:18:29,840 --> 00:18:30,600
I'm out!

385
00:18:34,470 --> 00:18:35,300
That is...

386
00:18:42,230 --> 00:18:44,040
I beg your pardon for disturbing you,
my Lady.

387
00:18:44,040 --> 00:18:45,040
I have something important to do.

388
00:18:45,040 --> 00:18:45,700
Excuse me.

389
00:18:52,050 --> 00:18:54,090
What a good kid.

390
00:18:55,040 --> 00:18:56,240
It'd be better

391
00:18:56,760 --> 00:18:58,490
that his last name was not Chen.

392
00:19:00,920 --> 00:19:02,040
That Luo,

393
00:19:02,120 --> 00:19:03,800
she even threatens me with her life

394
00:19:03,800 --> 00:19:05,610
for Chen Changsheng.

395
00:19:09,960 --> 00:19:10,920
Please ask the questions,

396
00:19:10,920 --> 00:19:13,160
Your Highness.

397
00:19:13,720 --> 00:19:15,080
Regarding the marriage,

398
00:19:15,080 --> 00:19:17,240
the first ones to be consulted
should be relatives and friends.

399
00:19:17,240 --> 00:19:20,440
Is there anyone against the marriage between Qiushan Jun

400
00:19:20,560 --> 00:19:21,870
and Xu Yourong?

401
00:19:25,320 --> 00:19:26,250
Weiyang Palace…

402
00:19:26,480 --> 00:19:27,650
Where is it?

403
00:19:28,320 --> 00:19:30,360
Next, the Heaven and Earth are asked.

404
00:19:30,360 --> 00:19:31,890
Is there anyone against it?

405
00:19:44,160 --> 00:19:46,360
Thirdly, to all the people in the world,

406
00:19:47,080 --> 00:19:48,610
is there anyone against it?

407
00:19:51,080 --> 00:19:51,720
All right.

408
00:19:51,960 --> 00:19:53,420
I'll grant the royal seal.

409
00:19:57,040 --> 00:19:57,920
I object!

410
00:19:57,260 --> 00:19:58,420
[Betrothal Contract]

411
00:20:09,940 --> 00:20:11,300
I object!

412
00:20:17,320 --> 00:20:21,320
[To be continued]

413
00:20:22,970 --> 00:20:24,500
Don't you all want more?

414
00:20:24,520 --> 00:20:26,650
I asked the white crane
to bring you a surprise.

415
00:20:26,650 --> 00:20:28,450
Please scan the QR code to watch.

416
00:20:30,180 --> 00:20:33,360
[In the next episode]

417
00:20:30,320 --> 00:20:32,680
How dare you three little brats

418
00:20:32,700 --> 00:20:34,140
speak rudely?

419
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:35,040
Today,

420
00:20:35,040 --> 00:20:37,640
I'll teach you a lesson
on behalf of your folks!

421
00:20:38,400 --> 00:20:40,330
On behalf of the Lishan Sword Sect,

422
00:20:40,400 --> 00:20:42,600
I'm asking the State Religious Academy

423
00:20:43,360 --> 00:20:44,280
to teach us something.

